22
00:03:08,813 --> 00:03:10,023
It's Yeong-u.

23
00:03:12,442 --> 00:03:13,610
What?

24
00:03:16,029 --> 00:03:17,322
My son is?

25
00:03:17,864 --> 00:03:18,740
Where's my husband?

26
00:03:19,324 --> 00:03:20,658
He's at the hospital.

27
00:03:21,951 --> 00:03:23,870
That rude wench.

28
