Wake him up!

73
00:06:09,994 --> 00:06:11,496
Come on, do something!

74
00:06:11,579 --> 00:06:12,789
Yeong-u, wake up!

75
00:06:13,498 --> 00:06:16,501
Wake him up!

76
00:06:17,668 --> 00:06:20,421
Don't fall asleep! Yeong-u!

